    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-10 items-stretch justify-center align-top md:space-x-10 md:space-y-0 md:p-4 md:flex-row md:text-left ">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 ">
        <h1 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold mb-6 md:text-left">
          Get to know me!
        </h1>
        <p>
          Hi, my name is Junichi and I am a{" "}
          <span class="font-bold">{"highly ambitious"}</span>,
          <span class="font-bold">{" self-motivated"}</span>, and
          <span class="font-bold">{" driven"}</span> Front end engineer
          based in Kanagawa, Japa.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
          I have a wide range of hobbies and passions that keep me busy.
          From reading, playing sports, traveling, to making YouTube videos,
          I am always seeking new experiences and love to keep myself
          engaged and learning new things.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
          I believe that you should{" "}
          <span class="font-bold text-teal-500">
            never stop growing
          </span>{" "}
          and that&#39;s what I strive to do, I have a passion for
          technology and a desire to always push the limits of what is
          possible. I am excited to see where my career takes me and am
          always open to new opportunities. ðŸ™‚
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center md:w-1/2 md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">My Skills</h1>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-row justify-center z-10 md:justify-start">
          {skills.map((item, idx) => {
            return (
              <p
               
                class="bg-gray-200 px-4 py-2 mr-2 mt-2 text-gray-500 rounded font-semibold"
              >
                {item.skill}
              </p>
            )
          })}
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  <!-- </div> -->
  </section>
</MainLayout>